According to Duan Kaiyuan, staff of the Legal and Rights Protection Work Department of Yunnan Federation of Trade Unions, the Provincial General Administration will strengthen the dynamic management of difficult workers' files, promote the normalization of archiving work, timely integration into the support system for difficult workers who meet the conditions for filing; broaden the application channels for difficult workers, use WeChat to open an online filing service platform for difficult workers,
During the epidemic, it was difficult for workers to go abroad. In order to help workers in difficult positions relieve the pressure of life, Yunnan Province arranged more than 13 million yuan to send warm funds, according to the standard of 2,000 yuan per household for workers in difficult positions at the national level and 1,500 yuan per household for workers in difficult positions at the provincial level.
At the same time, the Provincial General Manager connects with various Internet recruitment platforms such as human resources departments and Zhilian recruitment, pushes recruitment information to difficult workers, and provides employment advice and career guidance services.